&lt;p&gt;We’re a Psychological Therapy service providing high Intensity CBT for a range of Anxiety Disorders. We’re looking for a Senior High –Intensity Specialist Therapist to deliver groups and individual CBT. The role involves supporting the High Intensity Therapists by providing supervision, leadership and contributing to the further development of the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 12th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
